    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Young Inuit:</strong> A breed known for its hunting skill. This Nin-Dog gains the following;</p><ul><li><p>Proficiency in Investigation and Stealth.</p></li><li><p>Expertise in Perception.</p></li><li><p><strong>+</strong>10 increase to their speed and ignores difficult terrain.</p></li><li><p>This breed can either Dash or Disengage at no action cost, once per round as part of one of their commands.</p></li><li><p>Beginning at 11th level, your Nin-Dog gains the benefits of your Wild Sense feature.</p></li></ul>",
